# Composer Guide — Stationery Ordering Platform

Agent-oriented reference for working on this codebase. For user-facing setup and screenshots, see [README.md](README.md).

## What this is

A bilingual (Traditional Chinese / English) stationery e-commerce app with a customer shop and a separate admin dashboard. Customers browse and cart as guests; invite-code login is required only at checkout. Admins manage orders, analytics, and fulfillment through `/admin`.

## Critical: Next.js 16

This project uses **Next.js 16**, which has breaking changes from earlier versions. Before changing routing, middleware, or server APIs, read the relevant guide in:

```
node_modules/next/dist/docs/
```

Also see [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md).

